
--Histogram Equalization--

Project 5)

Functions for implementation: 
  -calculate histogram
  -calculate CDF
  -calculate Look Up Table
  -equalize histogram
  

Techniques\ideas researched: 

	-atomicAdd to avoid race conditions
	-dividing histogram creation process and use multiple streams
	-parallel scan Brent - Kung
	-shared memory for CreateCDF 
	-Cudamallocmanaged not prefered
	-experimenting with different num threads, block and grid dimension
